data.chText: 第三的；第三位的；第三级的
data.enText: third in order, rank or importance
the tertiary sector (= the area of industry that deals with services rather than materials or goods)
tertiary education (= at university or college level)

tr: coming next after the second and just before the fourth in position

value.def: Tertiary means third in order, third in importance, or at a third stage of development.

example.ex: He must have come to know those philosophers through secondary or tertiary sources.
example.tran: 他一定是通过第二手或第三手资料了解那些哲学家的。

example.ex: ...the complementary tertiary colours, russet and olive green.
example.tran: 互补的三次色——赤褐色和橄榄绿

value.tran: 第三的;第三位的;第三阶段的

value.def: Tertiary education is education at university or college level.

value.boxr_value: in AM, use 美国英语用 higher education

trans: 职业专科学校(英国为16岁以上的人提供教育的学院，但并非大学)
